0xD264D4E1.name: SET_WEATHER_CYCLE_ENTRY

params.name: index
params.description: The index of the entry to set. Must be between 0 and 255

params.name: typeName
params.description: The name of the weather type for this cycle

params.name: timeMult
params.description: The relative duration of this cycle, which is multiplied by `msPerCycle` during ['APPLY_WEATHER_CYCLES'](#\_0x3422291C). Must be between 1 and 255

0xD264D4E1.resultsDescription: Returns true if all parameters were valid, otherwise false.
